FrontierVcsFile:3:wptx:system.verbs.builtins.tcp.im.builtinDrivers.jabber.code.examples.pubsub.readme

This table contains code which implements the Publish-Subscribe client for Radio Userland over Jabber.

Make the pubsubPublishHandler an "iq" handler for the namespace "radio:iq:pubsub", and use the pubsubSubscribe and pubsubUnsubscribe code to send out the appropriate requests to your bridge.

Documentation in the style of DocServer has been included in the pubsubDocs subtable for the relevant scripts.


